OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FAn indoor snowboarding centre has been
OL,7,Ffined more than #100,000 after a 12-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy died in an accident on a
OL,9,Fski slope.
OL,11,FThe SnowDome in Tamworth was fined for
OL,12,Fbreaching health and safety
OL,13,Fregulations over the death of Louis
OL,14,FWatkiss.
OL,16,FLouis, from Sutton Coldfield, died
OL,17,Fafter colliding with a staff member at
OL,18,FTamworth SnowDome in September 2021.
