OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FThe three directors for SnowDome
OL,7,Fdescribed the business as a "small
OL,8,Fbusiness with a strong family feel".
OL,10,FThe court heard the company suffered
OL,11,Ffinancially during lockdown - and
OL,12,Fduring the riots in August after a
OL,13,Fhotel next door was looted.
OL,15,FThey said they are "forever deeply
OL,16,Fashamed" and that "responsibility will
OL,17,Fsit firmly on our shoulders
OL,18,Fforevermore".
