OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FOutside Telford Magistrates' Court on
OL,7,FWednesday, Louis' father Chris said:
OL,8,F"We want to thank HSE (Health Safety
OL,9,FExecutive) for getting a prosecution,
OL,10,Feven though the fine is ridiculous and
OL,11,Fis not appropriate to a child's death."
OL,13,FHe added: "You don't expect your child
OL,14,Fto go to a leisure centre, wind up
OL,15,Fdead, and there be no custodial
OL,16,Fsentence - just a fine, a slap on the
OL,17,Fwrist and get on with it."
