OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FLouis was at a friend's birthday
OL,7,Ftobogganing (sledding) party and was
OL,8,Ftravelling down the slope on a plastic
OL,9,Fsled.
OL,11,FHe crashed with the centre's
OL,12,Foperations manager Joseph Dibb, who
OL,13,Ffell backwards onto him. Louis
OL,14,Fsuffered skull fractures and died at
OL,15,Fthe scene.
OL,17,FTobogganing is no longer on offer at
OL,18,Fthe SnowDome. Helmets are now worn on
OL,19,Fevery activity including ice skating,
OL,20,Fthe centre said.
