OL,6,FThe court also saw CCTV footage of a
OL,7,Fsome collisions and near misses
OL,8,Fbetween staff and customers in the two
OL,9,Fweeks before Louis died.
OL,11,FIn his sentencing remarks, Judge Kevin
OL,12,FGrego said SnowDome had failed to
OL,13,Fconduct safe provision of activities,
OL,14,Fincluding tobogganing.
OL,16,FLouis' family will now wait until next
OL,17,Fyear for the inquest into his death.
