OL,6,FHis father Chris paid tribute to
OL,7,FLouis, who would have been 16 this
OL,8,Fyear: "He was a lovely lad, full of
OL,9,Flife, talented, very good at the
OL,10,Fsaxophone, intriguing, interested in
OL,11,Fthe world, brave courageous.
OL,13,F"We did some wicked and wild things
OL,14,Ftogether as a family, and him and I on
OL,15,Four own. It's just a sad sad loss. The
OL,16,Fworld's been robbed of a lovely lad."
OL,18,FHis mother Natalie added that he "had
OL,19,Fa huge circle of friends", who he had
OL,20,Fknown since nursery.
