OL,6,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) found SnowDome
OL,8,FLimited failed to ensure the safety of
OL,9,Fits customers, including Louis, while
OL,10,Fthey were undertaking tobogganing at
OL,11,Fthe venue.
