OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FThe HSE investigation also found that
OL,7,FSnowDome did not have a suitable and
OL,8,Fsufficient risk assessment for
OL,9,Ftobogganing activities and had not
OL,10,Ffully considered all persons likely to
OL,11,Fbe on the slope during tobogganing. As
OL,12,Fa result, there was no safe system of
OL,13,Fwork, information, instruction,
OL,14,Ftraining or supervision to manage the
OL,15,Frisk of collisions between toboggans
OL,16,Fand pedestrians.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
