OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,FNathan Cook, senior enforcement lawyer
OL,7,Ffor HSE said: "Louis went to a
OL,8,Ffriend's birthday party at the
OL,9,FSnowDome and should have returned home
OL,10,Fsafely to his family after an
OL,11,Fenjoyable occasion.
OL,13,F"Tragically, due to the failings of
OL,14,FSnowDome Limited, this did not happen.
OL,15,FLouis's death could have been
OL,16,Fprevented if the company had
OL,17,Fadequately assessed and controlled the
OL,18,Frisks associated with tobogganing
OL,19,Factivities.
