OL,3,CIndoor ski centre fined #100k after
OL,4,Cboy, 12, died in slope crash
OL,6,F"This should act as a reminder that
OL,7,Fvenues and employers must ensure
OL,8,Fsuitable and sufficient risk
OL,9,Fassessments are in place and employees
OL,10,Fare provided with sufficient safe
OL,11,Fsystems of work, information,
OL,12,Finstructions, training, and
OL,13,Fsupervision."
OL,15,FIn a statement, the Directors of the
OL,16,FSnowDome said: "Louis Watkiss should
OL,17,Fhave returned safely to his family
OL,18,Fafter tobogganing at the SnowDome. The
OL,19,Ffact that he didn't is something for
OL,20,Fwhich we will be forever remorseful."
