OL,6,F"We know we can never change what has
OL,7,Fhappened, and this heart-breaking
OL,8,Fknowledge is why we have always
OL,9,Faccepted full responsibility for this
OL,10,Fterrible tragedy.
OL,12,F"Louis and his family are constantly
OL,13,Fin our thoughts, and he will never be
OL,14,Fforgotten by anyone at the SnowDome."
OL,16,FSince his death, Louis's parents have
OL,17,Fcampaigned to make helmets mandatory
OL,18,Ffor children at indoor ski slopes.
